data.description: *inside pictures coming soon* Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Barrington Hall subdivision! Built in 2006, this stunning all-brick 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. Step into the spacious interior, where you'll find attention to detail at every turn. Entertain guests in style in the large backyard oasis, complete with a saltwater pool, fire pit, and covered deck area. Whether you're hosting poolside gatherings or cozy nights by the fire, this outdoor space is sure to impress. Enjoy the convenience of a sprinkler system and landscaping lights, enhancing the beauty of the lush surroundings. Plus, with the AC units replaced in 2019 and 2020, you can stay cool and comfortable year-round. Beautiful Barrington Hall Golf Club only 3 minutes away! Don't miss your chance to call this impeccable home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience luxury living at its finest! Listing Agent is a Licensed Lender NMLS#2518465 Gary Kimbler 478-733-0555
